{"tid":1705072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1111 交通狀況","createTime":"2019-11-11T00:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T00:33:21.000Z","uid":82639,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b932ade4b3eddcd725034b3e58e6d4e7fbc197","tid":1705072,"uid":82639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:14:53.000Z","msg":"我明白大家對有人中鎗好有反應。<br />\n今日要罷，同被罷<br />\n<br />\n我想大家 作為仲返工既和理非<br />\n請你將而家交通狀況報出黎 黨鐵app不可信。<br />\n我相信當大家知 周圍都無車 就會被罷工<br />\n<br />\n我自己就收到訊息<br />\n荃灣線去中環，葵興停曬，趕人落車，4防暴。葵芳唔比入<br />\n觀塘線停（未有詳情）<br />\n東鐵火炭以北無服務（黨鐵官方）<br />\n<br />\n利申，卧床軍師，我今日病，老闆已經將我個名比左部門祕書，等乞米。"},{"pid":"893522ca25e06680f6fa701b96ccfa6022573272","tid":1705072,"uid":333376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:15:39.000Z","msg":"西鐵暫停"},{"pid":"9fe0149b7033ceed4913b1d7ff925bd3f273fb29","tid":1705072,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:15:45.000Z","msg":"港島線咩情況"},{"pid":"e0af43601dc3a7682149be77f723b8b82e564da4","tid":1705072,"uid":122033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:16:38.000Z","msg":"東區走廊？"},{"pid":"76b78ccdbf58e30abcb91fc35727175113689d10","tid":1705072,"uid":198355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:17:39.000Z","msg":"好似好順"},{"pid":"352563d50b057b09dfdee2c5bb8adb27a662af0a","tid":1705072,"uid":288014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:19:10.000Z","msg":"紅色好順"},{"pid":"0e9457b495a13d9244bbfb480f17e79bbb54c046","tid":1705072,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:19:22.000Z","msg":"我用最卑微嘅心，求吓咁多位<br />\n<br />\n香港人，忍無可忍！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb4c9a292c4cbec55cd08b8c3caf3dcee6188e47","tid":1705072,"uid":1485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid